task.summary:
Default layouts file working with index
Also including new empty user account pages

User registration
Can create users in the database using the registration form

User login
Can login to the page. Register and Login buttons are then hidden from the main menu

User logout
Clicking logout on the main page logs the user out of the site and shows the login/register buttons

Highscores shown on the main page
Logged in users only. Non logged in users' scores don't get tracked.
